{#
stub_retry_hint.jinja2 — Stub Retry Prompt Hint Template
SPDX-License-Identifier: Proprietary
Copyright (c) 2025 Novatrax Labs

Renders a structured LLM prompt hint listing all auto-generated stub files
that require real implementations.  Groups stubs by module category and
provides per-file symbol export requirements for targeted LLM replacement.

Template Variables:
- grouped_stubs: Dict mapping category name → list of (path, symbols, content) tuples
#}
IMPORTANT: The following files are placeholder stubs that MUST be replaced with real implementations:

{% for group_name, group_files in grouped_stubs.items() %}
=== {{ group_name | upper }} FILES ===
{% for path, symbols, content in group_files %}
  - {{ path }}: must export {{ symbols }}
{% if content %}
    Current stub content (first 10 lines):
{% for line in content.splitlines()[:10] %}
    | {{ line }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% endfor %}
Generate complete, production-ready implementations for each stub file listed above.
Requirements:
- Use async SQLAlchemy 2.x sessions for database operations (session.execute(select(...)))
- Use Pydantic v2 models with Field(...) constraints for schemas
- Use FastAPI dependency injection (Depends()) for route handlers
- Do NOT use pass, ..., return None, TODO, FIXME, or raise NotImplementedError
